Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Canadian Pacific Plaza is not just an office building, its an experience! Consisting of 36,000 SF of dining and lifestyle amenities, you have everything you need for your work day. CPP provides the opportunity to unwind with a colleague in the new tenant lounge, grab a Starbucks drink on your way to a meeting or enjoy a fresh lunch at Greenfield. Take time for yourself at Take Care Chiropractic, schedule your next hair appointment at Madison & Co. and squeeze in a 30 minute personal training session at Discover Strength. Experience how Canadian Pacific Plaza caters to you!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Wells Fargo Plaza is a 24-story Class A high-rise located in Bloomington, Minnesota. It encompasses 17 manicured acres and consists of 458,702 SF of office and retail space. Amenity rich, Wells Fargo Plaza is in proximity of over 50 dining, shopping, gas/grocery, and services within a 2.0 mile drive radius. With a high-end tenant conference facility and training room, Wells Fargo Plaza aims to deliver first-class tenant service coupled with an unbeatable workplace environment, including a common 'link' between buildings and an outdoor plaza. The outdoor courtyard area features meeting and dining spaces including WiFi, in addition to a fire-pit enhanced recreational venue for small gatherings and events.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: A stunning 355,000 SF building that achieves a higher level of excellence in architectural design. As visitors and tenants enter the three level atrium lobby of the Colonnade, they are welcomed by lush greenery, reflective pools and quiet sitting areas. The Colonnade features a fitness facility with lockers and showers, a cafe, conferencing facilities, sundry shop, on site security, and covered climate control parking all as building amenities. Tenants at the Colonnade also have numerous retail and dining options in the West End neighborhood.
